These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-1::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, dressmaker
The people have 2 different hobbies: singing, cooking
1. the dressmaker is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is singing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Job           | dressmaker | designer |
| Hobby   | cooking     | singing  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-2::.
There 2 different types of food: lime, pumpkin
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, motorbike
1. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the left of the person eating lime##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |
| Food         | pumpkin   | lime      |
| Transport   | airplane | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-3::.
There are 2 different nationalities: british, chinese
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, subway
1. the british is somewhere to the right of the person driving the boat##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2    |
| Nationality   | chinese | british    |
| Transport     | boat | subway |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-4::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: musical, zombie
There 2 different types of food: radish, plum
1. the person eating plum is somewhere to the right of the person watching musical movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |
| Movie-Genre   | musical   | zombie |
| Food   | radish | plum |

 #################################

 
